{"word":"διαλυμαίνομαι","slug":"διαλυμαίνομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαλυμαίνομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to maltreat shamefully, undo utterly</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to cheat grossly</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to falsify, corrupt</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>no <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a> occurs, but <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>διαλελυμασμένος</el> is used in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> sense, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; aor1 <el>διελυμάνθην</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}